latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Besides all the love you shower your doggo with, a very important part of being a pet parent is to take proper care of them. This starts with providing your dog with the right nutrition.

Knowing the importance of right nutrition, we understand that it can be very tedious to choose and pick out the perfect food for your pup. So here we have reviewed the @purinaproplanindia's range of dog food from the house of Nestle. Their unique formula is prepared with quality ingredients like real Chicken, cereal, beet pulp fiber, essential vitamins and minerals etc, ensuring that your furballs get complete and balanced nutrition at every stage of their life.

Go ahead and try @purinaproplanindia dog food range and see the difference yourself.

latestPosts.caption:
The weekend Shakira and I was manifesting came true! 🐾✨
We spent the best time at @petfedindia Summer Camp at Pullman, Aerocity — and oh, what a day it was! From endless belly rubs, treats, games, to meeting new furry friends — every moment was worth the wag. 🐶💛

Big cheers to all the amazing pet parents we met & to everyone who gave our floofs so much love. 🥹
Weekends like this remind us — happiness really does have paws!

If you were there too, drop a 🐾 in the comments! Let’s relive the cutest summer day! 🌞✨
